作。", "block_bbox": [169, 1973, 1604, 2208], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "本书是作者在南开大学职攻读博士学位时完成的论文，文中对中古时期杜氏家庭各个郡望及其房支历史变迁的全面考察。着眼于杜氏一姓自秦汉以来特别是永嘉之乱后的文化、衍变和一些主干家庭的变迁，以及杜氏家庭史。立足于传统", "block_bbox": [169, 2227, 1605, 2399], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1719, 708, 1794, 1398], "block_id": 7, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "四一〇", "block_bbox": [1721, 2027, 1772, 2142], "block_id": 8, "block_order": null}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9468181133270264, "coordinate": [169.25885009765625, 1973.54638671875, 1604.259033203125, 2208.330078125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9345937371253967, "coordinate": [169.92279052734375, 2227.775146484375, 1605.75, 2399.604736328125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8317208886146545, "coordinate": [245.280029296875, 230.4722900390625, 1478.8056640625, 1431.068603515625]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7384387850761414, "coordinate": [642.574951171875, 1565.7861328125, 1130.2646484375, 1635.24462890625]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7084741592407227, "coordinate": [252.60345458984375, 1720.891357421875, 1298.767578125, 1765.3017578125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6146346926689148, "coordinate": [255.048583984375, 1849.119140625, 1021.329833984375, 1890.24560546875]}, {"cls_id": 18, "label": "aside_text", "score": 0.6093779802322388, "coordinate": [1719.093994140625, 708.823974609375, 1794.181396484375, 1398.674072265625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5814664959907532, "coordinate": [255.54498291015625, 1785.275634765625, 945.2147827148438, 1826.447509765625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5804497003555298, "coordinate": [260.50128173828125, 1913.10302734375, 431.212646484375, 1953.50244140625]}, {"cls_id": 18, "label": "aside_te